% Source inspiration: official 2D PWR pin-cell burnup example and CSG geometry guide.
% Intentional simplification: independently written two-surface model; no pin, set, or run cards.
% Expected findings: none for the documented first parser milestone.

/* This confirmed Serpent block-comment form is intentionally ignored.
   It also verifies that newline locations remain stable after preprocessing. */

surf fuelsurf cyl 0.0 0.0 0.40
surf outersurf sqc 0.0 0.0 0.65

cell fuelcell 0 fuel -fuelsurf
cell watercell 0 water fuelsurf -outersurf
cell outsidecell 0 outside outersurf

mat fuel -10.0
92235.09c -0.04
92238.09c -0.84
8016.09c -0.12

mat water -1.0
1001.09c -0.1119
8016.09c -0.8881
